1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,627
Previously on Seducing Drake Palma.

2
00:00:02,836 --> 00:00:04,396
Would you look at that?

3
00:00:04,421 --> 00:00:06,272
Drake’s your tutor.

4
00:00:06,297 --> 00:00:07,590
You’re really meant to be!

5
00:00:07,632 --> 00:00:08,695
By the way,

6
00:00:08,720 --> 00:00:10,360
don’t you dare seduce Drake.

7
00:00:10,385 --> 00:00:11,569
Excuse me,

8
00:00:11,594 --> 00:00:13,930
why would I have to
seduce Drake Palma?

9
00:00:15,733 --> 00:00:17,235
He’s my boyfriend!

10
00:00:18,018 --> 00:00:19,686
Wow!

11
00:00:19,728 --> 00:00:22,437
I already told
Uncle Steve we’re going!

12
00:00:22,462 --> 00:00:25,992
I told him we’re having lunch with them
because of our group project!

13
00:00:27,819 --> 00:00:29,429
Ouch! Let me do it!

14
00:00:33,099 --> 00:00:35,593
He’s my partner for the
acquaintance party.

15
00:00:35,775 --> 00:00:36,834
Show us.

16
00:00:36,859 --> 00:00:39,993
No, as in I won’t
go to that party!

17
00:00:40,018 --> 00:00:41,436
What if we go together?

18
00:01:29,881 --> 00:01:31,382
Am I not dreaming?

19
00:01:31,800 --> 00:01:34,719
Is Drake Palma really
in front of me?

20
00:01:35,303 --> 00:01:36,304
Follow me.

21
00:01:39,226 --> 00:01:40,686
Am I seeing things?

22
00:01:40,928 --> 00:01:42,180
It is Drake!

23
00:01:46,940 --> 00:01:48,316
Aww...

24
00:01:48,592 --> 00:01:50,511
He looks good in his outfit.

25
00:01:51,751 --> 00:01:54,390
His handsome look
makes me weak.

26
00:02:05,703 --> 00:02:06,703
Are you okay?

27
00:02:15,051 --> 00:02:16,351
What’s wrong with you?

28
00:03:14,981 --> 00:03:17,191
Should I talk to him?

29
00:03:24,078 --> 00:03:26,422
What made you change your mind?

30
00:03:30,835 --> 00:03:32,879
Aya, tell Alys that Drake
might be running late.

31
00:03:33,421 --> 00:03:35,106
Oh, Uncle!
It’s totally fine.

32
00:03:35,131 --> 00:03:38,384
Just let him be so
there’ll be romantic entrance.

33
00:03:38,635 --> 00:03:40,762
Alys thinks she
doesn’t have a date.

34
00:03:40,970 --> 00:03:43,524
But surprise—she does!

35
00:03:44,002 --> 00:03:45,837
Aya, you know everything!

36
00:03:47,018 --> 00:03:48,645
Of course, Uncle. It’s me.

37
00:03:48,670 --> 00:03:50,130
Aya, Drake’s here.

38
00:03:50,563 --> 00:03:52,961
- I have to go.
- Okay, Uncle. Bye!

39
00:03:57,237 --> 00:03:58,237
Drake...

40
00:04:00,034 --> 00:04:01,524
Drake, aren’t you going to the party?

41
00:04:03,952 --> 00:04:06,297
Drake, I know you want
to come with us to Taiwan.

42
00:04:07,288 --> 00:04:09,249
Alright, I’m letting you.
I’ll talk to your aunt.

43
00:04:09,274 --> 00:04:11,250
Follow us to
Taiwan, 5:00 AM flight.

44
00:04:11,459 --> 00:04:12,459
Really?

45
00:04:12,669 --> 00:04:14,087
But go to the party first.

46
00:04:15,338 --> 00:04:16,338
You should pick up Alys.

47
00:04:18,758 --> 00:04:20,093
You can wear this.

48
00:04:21,928 --> 00:04:23,888
Otherwise, don’t expect a ticket.

49
00:04:27,828 --> 00:04:28,828
Ugh!

50
00:04:31,208 --> 00:04:32,959
Hey. Hello?

51
00:04:33,616 --> 00:04:35,031
Answer me!

52
00:04:35,817 --> 00:04:37,555
Don’t you understand my question?

53
00:05:29,703 --> 00:05:33,504
I love you, Drake Palma!

54
00:05:47,169 --> 00:05:48,169
Hi.

55
00:05:49,208 --> 00:05:50,208
Hey.

56
00:05:55,183 --> 00:05:56,606
I’m so awesome!

57
00:05:59,783 --> 00:06:00,783
Well?

58
00:06:01,645 --> 00:06:04,215
My date tonight is
so handsome, right?

59
00:06:05,350 --> 00:06:07,238
What can you say, Kei?

60
00:06:09,494 --> 00:06:10,777
Like I care!

61
00:06:11,579 --> 00:06:13,645
You probably forced
Drake to come.

62
00:06:14,832 --> 00:06:16,459
I know your tricks!

63
00:06:19,379 --> 00:06:20,379
Oh, please.

64
00:06:20,404 --> 00:06:23,668
I can hear the jealousy in your voice
because Drake is my partner.

65
00:06:24,300 --> 00:06:25,343
So, cut it out.

66
00:06:26,344 --> 00:06:28,543
I am the queen of the night.

67
00:06:37,313 --> 00:06:38,313
Next!

68
00:06:44,028 --> 00:06:45,405
Hey, Drake. Let’s take a photo.

69
00:06:46,844 --> 00:06:49,263
Uh, never mind.
He doesn’t want to.

70
00:06:49,992 --> 00:06:51,411
He doesn’t want to.

71
00:06:53,646 --> 00:06:55,681
Well, you didn’t say anything!

72
00:06:55,706 --> 00:06:57,250
How would I know
you were up for it?

73
00:06:59,085 --> 00:07:00,814
Closer!
Come on, miss, closer!

74
00:07:04,257 --> 00:07:05,341
Closer still!

75
00:07:08,356 --> 00:07:10,400
This is three inches close!

76
00:07:11,597 --> 00:07:13,393
A little closer, miss!

77
00:07:32,618 --> 00:07:34,086
I can’t believe it.

78
00:07:35,496 --> 00:07:37,969
He picked me up,

79
00:07:38,958 --> 00:07:44,039
helped me up, and
put his arm around me.

80
00:07:44,464 --> 00:07:45,571
What happened?

81
00:07:45,852 --> 00:07:47,571
He’s not allergic to me anymore?

82
00:07:48,968 --> 00:07:49,969
Alys!

83
00:07:50,261 --> 00:07:51,596
Hey, Alys, what’s up?

84
00:07:54,713 --> 00:07:55,938
Why are you ignoring me?

85
00:07:58,311 --> 00:07:59,604
Hey, what’s wrong?

86
00:08:00,313 --> 00:08:01,439
What did I do?

87
00:08:01,689 --> 00:08:02,815
What do you think?

88
00:08:03,316 --> 00:08:04,567
You ditched me!

89
00:08:05,318 --> 00:08:06,502
You gave me false hope!

90
00:08:06,527 --> 00:08:10,323
What do you mean false hope?

91
00:08:10,573 --> 00:08:11,574
You’re right.

92
00:08:11,574 --> 00:08:14,327
I waited for you at home
and you never showed up!

93
00:08:15,650 --> 00:08:17,151
You left me hanging.

94
00:08:19,081 --> 00:08:21,042
Aya said you’re going with Drake.

95
00:08:21,417 --> 00:08:22,735
So I just went with her.

96
00:08:23,976 --> 00:08:24,729
Huh?

97
00:08:24,754 --> 00:08:25,836
Okay, thank you.

98
00:08:28,007 --> 00:08:29,217
Brother...

99
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:31,532
Bro, your phone’s so cool!

100
00:08:31,590 --> 00:08:33,175
The graphics are awesome!

101
00:08:33,876 --> 00:08:34,930
Here.

102
00:08:35,681 --> 00:08:36,696
Is this okay?

103
00:08:38,345 --> 00:08:39,471
Hey, CB!

104
00:08:40,353 --> 00:08:41,562
Aya Pineda?

105
00:08:42,688 --> 00:08:44,399
She’s that pretty weirdo, right?

106
00:08:51,739 --> 00:08:52,990
Blank message?

107
00:08:54,784 --> 00:08:56,369
Fine.
I’ll be straightforward.

108
00:08:57,128 --> 00:08:59,962
Don’t invite Alys.

109
00:09:00,570 --> 00:09:03,602
Drake is her partner in AP!

110
00:09:04,794 --> 00:09:05,795
Sent!

111
00:09:05,795 --> 00:09:07,821
Wow! All caps? Intense!

112
00:09:18,724 --> 00:09:24,886
What about me?
Should you be my partner?

113
00:09:38,327 --> 00:09:40,997
Fine! You’re my AP partner now!

114
00:09:42,623 --> 00:09:43,624
Yes!

115
00:09:47,628 --> 00:09:49,088
This phone is awesome!

116
00:09:50,631 --> 00:09:52,133
Aya said that?

117
00:09:53,676 --> 00:09:55,678
Seriously, Aya Pineda?!

118
00:09:56,470 --> 00:09:59,432
She’s still pushing this
matchmaking with Drake!

119
00:09:59,849 --> 00:10:02,935
I thought Drake really
came to pick me up!

120
00:10:03,269 --> 00:10:05,062
Ugh! I almost fell for it!

121
00:10:05,575 --> 00:10:08,384
- Had I known that Aya didn’t tell you-
- Oh, whatever!

122
00:10:08,941 --> 00:10:11,777
You didn’t even wonder
why I changed partners?

123
00:10:12,028 --> 00:10:14,322
You didn’t even call or text me?

124
00:10:16,033 --> 00:10:18,009
You’re the worst
best friend, Sheen!

125
00:10:18,951 --> 00:10:20,161
We’re done!

126
00:10:23,706 --> 00:10:26,626
You know that will never happen.

127
00:10:27,627 --> 00:10:29,170
You’re my best friend for a reason.

128
00:10:30,087 --> 00:10:32,256
You’ll be with me forever.
We can’t break up.

129
00:10:32,256 --> 00:10:33,382
You have to stick with me.

130
00:10:35,339 --> 00:10:37,200
It’s hard to be his best friend.

131
00:10:37,470 --> 00:10:40,097
Why did I agree to
be Sheen’s best friend?

132
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:43,434
I should have been patient
and waited to be his girlfriend.

133
00:10:43,694 --> 00:10:46,697
Why did he become classmates
with Kei last year?

134
00:10:46,811 --> 00:10:48,530
She got ahead of me.

135
00:10:50,261 --> 00:10:52,295
I’m sorry, okay?

136
00:10:53,194 --> 00:10:55,241
Don’t be mad, please?

137
00:10:55,609 --> 00:10:56,735
You’re being silly.

138
00:10:57,124 --> 00:10:58,124
Sheen!

139
00:10:59,367 --> 00:11:01,327
I have to go. Are we good?

140
00:11:01,786 --> 00:11:02,786
Hmm?

141
00:11:03,162 --> 00:11:04,747
I still have something
to do backstage.

142
00:11:05,748 --> 00:11:07,358
- Go ahead!
- Save a dance for me.

143
00:11:20,638 --> 00:11:22,264
Sheen’s so annoying!

144
00:11:23,099 --> 00:11:24,475
He left me here!

145
00:11:25,059 --> 00:11:26,059
What a jerk!

146
00:11:27,895 --> 00:11:28,895
Hi.

147
00:11:34,819 --> 00:11:36,404
Here, allow me.

148
00:11:37,446 --> 00:11:39,407
You’re such a messy eater!

149
00:11:48,124 --> 00:11:49,375
Aren’t you feeling giddy?

150
00:11:51,460 --> 00:11:52,645
Who are you?

151
00:11:52,670 --> 00:11:53,772
You don’t know me?

152
00:11:54,380 --> 00:11:56,803
I’m the Student Council
Vice President.

153
00:11:57,925 --> 00:11:59,093
Okay.

154
00:12:01,637 --> 00:12:04,350
Kent Justin Valdez, at your service!

155
00:12:11,981 --> 00:12:13,545
I just came from the bathroom!

156
00:12:15,053 --> 00:12:16,798
You’re fun to talk to.

157
00:12:16,823 --> 00:12:18,504
Did I say something funny?

158
00:12:18,529 --> 00:12:19,463
Good question!

159
00:12:19,495 --> 00:12:22,331
Actually, I’ve been watching you.

160
00:12:22,742 --> 00:12:25,369
I mean, you just stayed in your seat.

161
00:12:25,870 --> 00:12:27,121
Are you a stalker?

162
00:12:29,665 --> 00:12:30,665
Admirer.

163
00:12:31,417 --> 00:12:32,648
I’m good-looking, after all.

164
00:12:35,963 --> 00:12:37,437
You’re so full of yourself!

165
00:12:37,462 --> 00:12:39,976
Go away! I’m eating!

166
00:12:41,635 --> 00:12:43,304
And it was lovely meeting you, too.

167
00:12:43,888 --> 00:12:44,888
See you around!

168
00:12:52,521 --> 00:12:53,521
Who was that?

169
00:12:53,939 --> 00:12:54,940
So annoying!

170
00:12:55,649 --> 00:12:57,629
This is all Sheen’s fault!

171
00:12:58,152 --> 00:13:00,905
He left me, and now I
had to deal with that creep!

172
00:13:05,935 --> 00:13:06,935
Hey!

173
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:09,120
Hey!

174
00:13:13,417 --> 00:13:14,643
Whatever!

175
00:13:14,668 --> 00:13:16,796
You really think I wouldn’t
know about what you did.

176
00:13:17,421 --> 00:13:18,589
Come on, bestie!

177
00:13:19,924 --> 00:13:21,759
Have you eaten?
Main dish is good!

178
00:13:21,784 --> 00:13:22,868
- Let’s eat!
- No!

179
00:13:23,177 --> 00:13:25,144
But I’m sure you already ate.

180
00:13:25,387 --> 00:13:27,181
You’re being judgemental, bestie.

181
00:13:29,725 --> 00:13:30,618
Because --

182
00:13:30,643 --> 00:13:31,977
Where’s your date?

183
00:13:42,780 --> 00:13:44,566
Oh, he’s swarmed
by those “like” girls!

184
00:13:47,159 --> 00:13:48,918
Like dance with me?

185
00:13:49,245 --> 00:13:51,746
Like have you eaten?
Let’s eat together.

186
00:13:51,789 --> 00:13:53,746
Like dessert, Drake?

187
00:13:53,833 --> 00:13:54,833
You like?

188
00:14:07,341 --> 00:14:08,467
Excuse me…

189
00:14:09,348 --> 00:14:10,391
he’s my date!

190
00:14:13,894 --> 00:14:15,437
What’s with the glare?

191
00:14:15,479 --> 00:14:18,566
Do you want me to
poke your eyes and record it?

192
00:14:22,528 --> 00:14:23,671
Like, chill, bestie.

193
00:14:23,696 --> 00:14:25,030
I’ll handle this for you!

194
00:14:25,656 --> 00:14:27,533
Like, bestie, please no.

195
00:14:27,533 --> 00:14:28,909
So they’ll stop.

196
00:14:28,909 --> 00:14:30,035
Recording!

197
00:14:32,913 --> 00:14:36,083
Drake, I’m your date tonight, right?

198
00:14:40,004 --> 00:14:41,004
Tss.

199
00:14:43,465 --> 00:14:44,441
Did you see that?

200
00:14:44,466 --> 00:14:45,968
That was so embarrassing!

201
00:14:51,223 --> 00:14:52,241
Bestie, stop it.

202
00:14:52,266 --> 00:14:53,642
Oops, sorry!

203
00:14:54,143 --> 00:14:55,895
Hey, cut it out!

204
00:15:44,068 --> 00:15:45,068
Drake!

205
00:15:48,314 --> 00:15:49,314
Hey!

206
00:15:50,333 --> 00:15:51,333
Sshh.

207
00:16:20,354 --> 00:16:22,731
Drake, everyone’s staring!

208
00:16:23,107 --> 00:16:24,149
Don’t mind them.

209
00:16:24,775 --> 00:16:25,775
But…

210
00:16:33,242 --> 00:16:34,243
Those were three words.

211
00:16:34,243 --> 00:16:36,495
The longest phrase he said all night.

212
00:16:46,380 --> 00:16:47,506
Can I ask you something?

213
00:16:51,549 --> 00:16:53,051
Why are you dancing with me?

214
00:16:54,854 --> 00:16:56,272
Those girls are annoying.

215
00:16:57,850 --> 00:16:59,643
Am I not annoying?

216
00:17:00,962 --> 00:17:01,962
You’re annoying.

217
00:17:04,148 --> 00:17:05,190
But that’s fine.

218
00:17:07,500 --> 00:17:08,500
No.

219
00:17:08,532 --> 00:17:09,532
No.

220
00:17:09,792 --> 00:17:11,085
He is with Katrina.

221
00:17:11,600 --> 00:17:14,082
This is just a crush. Period!

222
00:17:15,743 --> 00:17:16,743
By the way,

223
00:17:17,036 --> 00:17:19,079
that pink tie looks good
on you.

224
00:18:12,132 --> 00:18:13,132
It’s done.

225
00:18:13,439 --> 00:18:14,439
Hmm?

226
00:18:19,681 --> 00:18:20,766
I’m so sorry!

227
00:18:35,322 --> 00:18:37,533
I finally got away!

228
00:18:38,338 --> 00:18:39,339
Drake is too much!

229
00:18:39,701 --> 00:18:41,203
He’s good at making
my heart race!

230
00:18:41,877 --> 00:18:42,877
Alys!

231
00:18:45,624 --> 00:18:46,624
Forget it, Sheen!

232
00:18:46,792 --> 00:18:47,835
Go back to the stage!

233
00:18:48,544 --> 00:18:51,713
Just because you’re the president,
you’re taking me for granted.

234
00:18:52,446 --> 00:18:53,446
Come on.

235
00:18:54,040 --> 00:18:55,040
That’s not true.

236
00:18:55,759 --> 00:18:56,759
Speak for yourself.

237
00:18:57,636 --> 00:18:59,731
You almost swapped
faces with Drake!

238
00:19:01,014 --> 00:19:02,965
Am I being replaced?

239
00:19:04,226 --> 00:19:06,353
Is Sheen my loves
getting jealous?

240
00:19:08,272 --> 00:19:09,272
Keep dreaming!

241
00:19:10,232 --> 00:19:11,650
Talking to him is useless.

242
00:19:21,243 --> 00:19:22,243
Shall we dance?

243
00:19:24,204 --> 00:19:25,414
Is he trying to make up to me?

244
00:19:26,290 --> 00:19:28,125
Or he doesn’t want
to lose to Drake?

245
00:19:40,137 --> 00:19:41,137
Hmm...

246
00:19:41,162 --> 00:19:42,997
What is he thinking?

247
00:19:43,418 --> 00:19:44,903
He’s giving that death stare.

248
00:19:45,851 --> 00:19:47,269
Whatever.

249
00:19:47,365 --> 00:19:49,192
I’ll just dance with Sheen my loves.

250
00:20:11,543 --> 00:20:14,206
Why does he seem sad?

251
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:17,257
Isn’t he happy dancing with me?

252
00:20:17,984 --> 00:20:18,984
Alys...

253
00:20:20,314 --> 00:20:21,917
Can I ask you something?

254
00:20:26,892 --> 00:20:29,061
Do you think I should go after Kei?

255
00:20:33,941 --> 00:20:35,108
Do you still love her?

256
00:20:36,652 --> 00:20:37,652
I do.

257
00:20:39,072 --> 00:20:40,072
A lot.

258
00:20:44,797 --> 00:20:46,424
I know, best friend.

259
00:20:47,829 --> 00:20:49,623
Fight for her, you silly.

260
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:53,377
You love her, right?

261
00:20:53,669 --> 00:20:54,669
Mmm.

262
00:20:56,338 --> 00:20:57,381
Don’t give up on her.

263
00:21:08,392 --> 00:21:09,392
All right.

264
00:21:10,102 --> 00:21:11,812
Thank you, Alys.
I’ll look for Kei.

265
00:21:11,812 --> 00:21:12,812
Wish me luck!

266
00:21:28,370 --> 00:21:29,370
By the way,

267
00:21:29,444 --> 00:21:31,149
that pink tie looks
good on you.

268
00:21:44,094 --> 00:21:45,094
11:00 PM.

269
00:21:45,470 --> 00:21:46,665
It’s going to take awhile.

270
00:21:47,431 --> 00:21:48,515
I can’t go home yet.

271
00:21:54,333 --> 00:21:57,044
Like who the heck
is that Alys Perez?

272
00:21:58,108 --> 00:21:59,751
Like I don’t know.

273
00:21:59,776 --> 00:22:01,737
Girl, she’s a snake!

274
00:22:02,018 --> 00:22:04,790
She’s dancing with Drake,
then now with Sheen?

275
00:22:05,365 --> 00:22:08,702
She is so annoying.

276
00:22:09,036 --> 00:22:11,872
Like I have something
in mind, girls!

277
00:22:11,897 --> 00:22:13,523
Like what?

278
00:22:14,374 --> 00:22:17,544
Let’s lock her up
in the stock room.

279
00:22:17,919 --> 00:22:19,004
She deserves it!

280
00:22:19,069 --> 00:22:21,398
That sounds like so much fun!

281
00:22:21,423 --> 00:22:23,133
I’m in that!

282
00:22:23,425 --> 00:22:24,425
Let’s go!

283
00:22:53,957 --> 00:22:56,720
Maybe if I wear this,
they won’t bother me anymore.

284
00:22:58,370 --> 00:23:00,399
Please!
Give me one more chance, Kei!

285
00:23:02,047 --> 00:23:03,462
I won’t screw up again!

286
00:23:04,329 --> 00:23:06,957
Sorry if I made the student council
my priority over you.

287
00:23:08,553 --> 00:23:09,553
Sheen...

288
00:23:09,606 --> 00:23:11,191
I know it’s cliché, but...

289
00:23:12,015 --> 00:23:14,643
it’s not you, it’s me.

290
00:23:15,852 --> 00:23:16,852
Please.

291
00:23:17,813 --> 00:23:19,915
Kei, just one more chance.

292
00:23:19,940 --> 00:23:20,940
I love you so much!

293
00:23:22,681 --> 00:23:24,277
We already talked about this.

294
00:23:25,445 --> 00:23:26,905
We’re done.

295
00:23:28,281 --> 00:23:29,699
You’re a good guy.

296
00:23:30,909 --> 00:23:32,994
You’ll find someone else, but...

297
00:23:34,037 --> 00:23:35,580
But I’m not the one for you.

298
00:23:35,997 --> 00:23:38,291
You’re the only one I want, Kei!

299
00:23:39,209 --> 00:23:40,293
Only you!

300
00:23:40,627 --> 00:23:42,295
I like someone else, Sheen.

301
00:23:43,130 --> 00:23:44,339
I’m really sorry.

302
00:23:44,714 --> 00:23:46,133
Do you really like Drake?

303
00:24:00,724 --> 00:24:03,102
I love you.
Remember that, Kei.

304
00:24:04,958 --> 00:24:06,442
I’ll do everything to
make you happy.

305
00:24:09,114 --> 00:24:10,449
You want me to be happy?

306
00:24:11,283 --> 00:24:14,090
Then tell Alys to
stay away from Drake.

307
00:24:18,073 --> 00:24:19,073
What, Sheen?

308
00:24:32,888 --> 00:24:36,141
Why does Sheen keep on chasing
someone who doesn’t like him?

309
00:24:37,350 --> 00:24:39,227
Why can’t he just
let Kei be with Drake?

310
00:24:41,646 --> 00:24:44,226
If Drake hadn’t
come into our lives,

311
00:24:44,592 --> 00:24:46,427
none of this would’ve happened.

312
00:24:48,098 --> 00:24:49,640
Especially how I feel.

313
00:24:55,952 --> 00:24:56,952
Let’s go.

314
00:25:03,168 --> 00:25:04,169
Like hey!

315
00:25:06,755 --> 00:25:07,755
What?

316
00:25:07,964 --> 00:25:10,046
Like someone’s looking for you.

317
00:25:10,467 --> 00:25:11,467
Who is it?

318
00:25:12,093 --> 00:25:14,304
Like do we even
look like we care?

319
00:25:14,554 --> 00:25:16,539
Just be thankful that
we even helped him.

320
00:25:17,057 --> 00:25:20,894
Like looking at your
ugly face is so like torture.

321
00:25:21,436 --> 00:25:22,562
Like yes!

322
00:25:23,185 --> 00:25:26,399
Like he even gave us this.

323
00:25:28,860 --> 00:25:31,238
Like thanks!

324
00:25:35,218 --> 00:25:37,345
Meet me inside the stockroom.

325
00:25:37,577 --> 00:25:38,678
Urgent.

326
00:25:38,703 --> 00:25:41,289
P.S. I am your secret admirer.

327
00:25:42,019 --> 00:25:43,103
Is this for real?

328
00:25:56,346 --> 00:25:57,430
Let’s go.

329
00:26:00,513 --> 00:26:03,433
Meet me inside the
stockroom. Urgent.

330
00:26:03,458 --> 00:26:07,212
P.S. I am your secret admirer.

331
00:26:14,707 --> 00:26:15,707
Hello?

332
00:26:17,312 --> 00:26:18,313
Hello?

333
00:26:21,997 --> 00:26:23,523
Anyone here?

334
00:26:27,002 --> 00:26:28,002
Hello?

335
00:26:39,389 --> 00:26:40,849
Hey! Wait!

336
00:26:41,224 --> 00:26:42,784
Someone’s in here!

337
00:26:42,809 --> 00:26:44,102
Why did you lock the door?

338
00:26:45,186 --> 00:26:47,022
OMG! How do I open this?!

339
00:26:47,564 --> 00:26:49,524
Hey! I’m stuck in here!

340
00:26:49,816 --> 00:26:51,151
Help!

341
00:26:51,669 --> 00:26:52,733
Where is Alys?

342
00:26:54,654 --> 00:26:56,364
Bee! I found you!

343
00:26:57,411 --> 00:26:58,412
Let’s do a slow dance!

344
00:26:58,587 --> 00:26:59,587
- Slow dance?
- I got this!

345
00:27:01,453 --> 00:27:02,453
There!

346
00:27:05,123 --> 00:27:09,380
This little troll
won’t stop following me!

347
00:27:09,878 --> 00:27:12,297
Bee, what’s with your face?

348
00:27:12,714 --> 00:27:14,232
Stop calling me Bee!

349
00:27:14,257 --> 00:27:16,760
I’m Aya! A-ya!

350
00:27:17,052 --> 00:27:18,303
You are Bee!

351
00:27:18,637 --> 00:27:20,513
‘Cause I’m your honey!

352
00:27:22,098 --> 00:27:23,516
Seriously?!

353
00:27:24,324 --> 00:27:25,951
What is your problem?!

354
00:27:27,437 --> 00:27:28,647
Relax, Aya babes!

355
00:27:29,022 --> 00:27:30,857
You’ll get wrinkles!

356
00:27:32,651 --> 00:27:35,362
Oh my God, Lord!

357
00:27:36,404 --> 00:27:38,323
- You’re so mean to me, Bee!
- Lord!

358
00:27:38,348 --> 00:27:41,232
- Please, Lord!
- I’m not a monster!

359
00:27:44,871 --> 00:27:47,307
Why, Lord?! Why?!

360
00:27:47,332 --> 00:27:48,667
Where’s Alys?

361
00:27:49,417 --> 00:27:50,502
I don’t know!

362
00:27:51,044 --> 00:27:52,629
I’ve been looking for her, too!

363
00:27:52,837 --> 00:27:54,427
She left her phone with me!

364
00:27:55,677 --> 00:27:56,685
Wait a minute.

365
00:27:57,133 --> 00:27:59,010
Why are you looking for my friend?

366
00:27:59,714 --> 00:28:00,757
Who are you?!

367
00:28:01,614 --> 00:28:04,033
So, they really went through
with their plan.

368
00:28:04,119 --> 00:28:06,538
Tss. Now, I need to find her.

369
00:28:10,068 --> 00:28:11,206
Bee?

370
00:28:11,231 --> 00:28:13,066
Bee, wait! Bee!

371
00:28:14,442 --> 00:28:15,819
Saint Collete.

372
00:28:16,528 --> 00:28:17,528
Saint Collete.

373
00:28:18,154 --> 00:28:19,406
Saint Collete, please!

374
00:28:20,365 --> 00:28:23,034
I don’t mind if you
show up right now.

375
00:28:23,034 --> 00:28:24,388
It’s okay with me.

376
00:28:24,420 --> 00:28:27,443
Just open this door, please!

377
00:28:58,134 --> 00:29:00,344
Thank you!

378
00:29:03,048 --> 00:29:04,284
What’s with these students?

379
00:29:04,309 --> 00:29:06,228
I said close it after!

380
00:29:08,110 --> 00:29:09,278
Not again!

381
00:29:14,544 --> 00:29:15,311
Wait—

382
00:29:15,336 --> 00:29:18,047
Wait—hold on!

383
00:29:20,258 --> 00:29:21,259
Pervert!

384
00:29:22,177 --> 00:29:23,178
Creep!

385
00:29:24,387 --> 00:29:26,473
You touched my boob!

386
00:29:27,891 --> 00:29:29,220
My most precious!

387
00:29:32,687 --> 00:29:34,439
You creep! Perv!

388
00:29:39,486 --> 00:29:40,612
Who are you?

389
00:29:41,874 --> 00:29:42,875
Are you a mascot?

390
00:29:45,629 --> 00:29:48,006
Who are you?
Take that mascot head off.

391
00:29:51,581 --> 00:29:54,918
Come on! I just want to
know who touched me first!

392
00:29:58,338 --> 00:30:00,398
You’re so annoying!

393
00:30:00,423 --> 00:30:02,008
Those like girls are annoying!

394
00:30:02,045 --> 00:30:05,131
And I’m an idiot
for ending up here!

395
00:30:05,156 --> 00:30:06,337
It’s so frustrating!

396
00:30:07,597 --> 00:30:08,603
I’m…

397
00:30:09,349 --> 00:30:10,353
Whatever.

398
00:30:11,851 --> 00:30:14,412
Hi, everyone! I know
everybody’s still having fun,

399
00:30:14,437 --> 00:30:15,814
but it’s 12:00 AM.

400
00:30:15,980 --> 00:30:17,565
It’s time to wrap things up.

401
00:30:20,693 --> 00:30:21,693
Maybe

402
00:30:22,445 --> 00:30:26,491
you're the ugliest in Saint Collete High,
that’s why you won’t show your face.

403
00:30:28,368 --> 00:30:30,595
Whatever! That’s okay.

404
00:30:30,620 --> 00:30:33,915
It’s better to look ugly than
have a personality like Drake Palma!

405
00:30:35,273 --> 00:30:36,816
He’s the one to blame.

406
00:30:37,658 --> 00:30:38,658
If it weren’t for him,

407
00:30:39,239 --> 00:30:41,325
my life wouldn’t get this messy!

408
00:30:41,589 --> 00:30:42,757
Sheen’s life, too!

409
00:30:44,509 --> 00:30:46,353
So, who are you?

410
00:30:47,337 --> 00:30:49,665
I promise I won’t tell.
Pinky swear!

411
00:30:52,225 --> 00:30:54,102
Like such a buzzkill!

412
00:30:54,540 --> 00:30:57,681
True! Like, can we extend?

413
00:30:57,981 --> 00:30:58,581
Sorry.

414
00:30:58,606 --> 00:31:01,017
But the party is officially over.
Thank you for coming.

415
00:31:03,361 --> 00:31:05,154
Like let’s just go home.

416
00:31:10,088 --> 00:31:11,131
I’m…

417
00:31:11,494 --> 00:31:12,537
Neil?

418
00:31:13,430 --> 00:31:14,598
Yeah, Neil.

419
00:31:16,833 --> 00:31:18,668
Do we even have a
batchmate named Neil?

420
00:31:20,495 --> 00:31:22,247
Hi, Neil. I’m Alys.

421
00:31:24,376 --> 00:31:25,425
Ahh!

422
00:31:26,175 --> 00:31:28,303
Creep!

423
00:31:28,667 --> 00:31:29,540
Wait!

424
00:31:29,564 --> 00:31:30,889
Why do you keep hitting me?

425
00:31:31,556 --> 00:31:33,099
That’s strike two!

426
00:31:33,099 --> 00:31:34,325
On my boob!

427
00:31:34,350 --> 00:31:35,579
What did I touch?

428
00:31:35,685 --> 00:31:37,687
I didn’t do anything!
Did I touch the wall?

429
00:31:38,730 --> 00:31:40,815
You’re shameless!
Creep!

430
00:31:40,840 --> 00:31:44,218
Perv! Liar! Thief! Forger!

431
00:31:44,243 --> 00:31:46,112
I’ll tell the whole world about this, Neil!

432
00:31:46,112 --> 00:31:48,197
Whatever-your-last-name-is!

433
00:31:48,222 --> 00:31:49,473
You’re disgusting!

434
00:31:58,294 --> 00:31:59,503
Where could Alys be?

435
00:32:00,451 --> 00:32:02,008
I haven’t seen Drake, too.

436
00:32:02,937 --> 00:32:05,618
Great, maybe she’s with him!

437
00:32:06,174 --> 00:32:07,400
This is exciting!

438
00:32:07,425 --> 00:32:08,425
Bee!

439
00:32:09,677 --> 00:32:10,762
Why are you smiling?

440
00:32:11,763 --> 00:32:13,473
Thinking of me already?

441
00:32:14,974 --> 00:32:17,352
Please, just leave me alone, Kent!

442
00:32:17,810 --> 00:32:18,810
Kent, right?!

443
00:32:18,853 --> 00:32:20,705
You even remembered my name!

444
00:32:20,730 --> 00:32:22,148
So I’m unforgettable?

445
00:32:22,523 --> 00:32:23,523
You’re so full of it!

446
00:32:23,816 --> 00:32:25,068
Leave me alone!

447
00:32:25,380 --> 00:32:27,153
Don’t push me away, Bee.

448
00:32:27,577 --> 00:32:29,412
I’ll only fall harder!

449
00:32:30,239 --> 00:32:31,449
What’s going on here?

450
00:32:32,367 --> 00:32:34,138
You’re the worst date, Sheen!

451
00:32:34,452 --> 00:32:36,371
You left me with this creep!

452
00:32:36,905 --> 00:32:38,181
- Unbelievable!
- Sorry!

453
00:32:38,206 --> 00:32:39,791
I was just dealing with so much!

454
00:32:40,083 --> 00:32:41,083
Whatever.

455
00:32:41,344 --> 00:32:43,596
Hey, Kent.
Why are you with Aya?

456
00:32:44,420 --> 00:32:45,755
I’m courting Aya!

457
00:32:49,842 --> 00:32:50,842
Ugh!

458
00:32:59,727 --> 00:33:00,853
Saint Collete!

459
00:33:00,895 --> 00:33:03,098
Thank you for the light!

460
00:33:03,123 --> 00:33:05,000
Thank you!

461
00:33:09,195 --> 00:33:10,405
Hello!

462
00:33:10,571 --> 00:33:12,115
Anyone out there?!

463
00:33:12,824 --> 00:33:15,076
Please! We’re stuck in here!

464
00:33:15,101 --> 00:33:16,928
We’re here!

465
00:33:16,953 --> 00:33:19,622
Open the door, please!

466
00:33:20,297 --> 00:33:21,760
- Help!
- Don’t bother to open it.

467
00:33:22,875 --> 00:33:23,875
It’s locked.

468
00:33:40,601 --> 00:33:43,354
Neil, do you have a phone?

469
00:33:44,272 --> 00:33:45,356
Do you have it with you?

470
00:33:46,190 --> 00:33:47,525
Let me call Aya.

471
00:33:49,027 --> 00:33:50,027
Low-batt.

472
00:33:55,408 --> 00:33:57,910
I said I’d be home by one.

473
00:33:58,020 --> 00:34:00,689
My parents are probably worried.

474
00:34:03,103 --> 00:34:04,563
I also have a flight.

475
00:34:04,588 --> 00:34:06,798
But I won’t make it
because of you.

476
00:34:08,880 --> 00:34:10,523
I shouldn’t have looked for you.

477
00:34:10,777 --> 00:34:13,105
I was just trying to help,
and now I’m the bad guy.

478
00:34:13,146 --> 00:34:15,189
Let’s just stay here ‘til morning.

479
00:34:20,349 --> 00:34:22,935
Neil, can I ask you something?

480
00:34:23,303 --> 00:34:24,554
Aren’t you already asking?

481
00:34:25,297 --> 00:34:26,757
So rude!

482
00:34:28,858 --> 00:34:29,984
You’re a guy, right?

483
00:34:32,063 --> 00:34:33,254
You want me to prove it?

484
00:34:33,279 --> 00:34:34,279
What the—?!

485
00:34:35,713 --> 00:34:36,713
You’re not worth it.

486
00:34:37,127 --> 00:34:38,127
Keep dreaming.

487
00:34:39,246 --> 00:34:41,665
He’s acting like Drake!

488
00:34:42,248 --> 00:34:44,917
But that’s impossible!

489
00:34:46,042 --> 00:34:47,627
He should be asleep by now.

490
00:34:47,652 --> 00:34:48,652
Hey!

491
00:34:49,045 --> 00:34:51,839
For your information,
I’m beautiful.

492
00:34:52,423 --> 00:34:54,008
You know Drake Palma?

493
00:34:55,927 --> 00:34:58,721
The arrogant and handsome guy
all the girls are chasing?

494
00:35:00,098 --> 00:35:01,224
He’s my boyfriend!

495
00:35:02,058 --> 00:35:03,768
He’s with me because I’m pretty!

496
00:35:08,940 --> 00:35:10,149
Why are you laughing?

497
00:35:10,525 --> 00:35:11,859
You don’t believe me?

498
00:35:12,378 --> 00:35:13,796
Why would I believe you?

499
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:15,571
We’re legit!

500
00:35:16,322 --> 00:35:18,741
I know Uncle Steve, his dad!

501
00:35:19,242 --> 00:35:21,661
And Aunt Katrina…
his secret rel—

502
00:35:21,861 --> 00:35:25,115
I mean, stepmom...

503
00:35:25,140 --> 00:35:26,558
His future stepmom!

504
00:35:28,960 --> 00:35:31,629
So, about Drake.

505
00:35:32,713 --> 00:35:33,713
Do you like him?

506
00:35:35,640 --> 00:35:36,640
Uh…

507
00:35:37,969 --> 00:35:39,691
A little.

508
00:35:43,266 --> 00:35:44,767
He’s really handsome.

509
00:35:45,101 --> 00:35:47,270
Even if he always
looks like someone just died.

510
00:35:49,480 --> 00:35:50,773
He’s smart, too.

511
00:35:51,274 --> 00:35:53,317
He sleeps a lot but
still aces everything.

512
00:35:56,068 --> 00:35:57,611
Tss. I’m right.

513
00:35:57,751 --> 00:36:00,394
Everything she likes about me
is superficial.

514
00:36:00,908 --> 00:36:03,472
My good looks and perfect grades.

515
00:36:03,619 --> 00:36:06,205
She’s no different from those
annoying “like girls”.

516
00:36:06,205 --> 00:36:08,370
Or maybe worse.

517
00:36:09,667 --> 00:36:11,752
And just between us, okay?

518
00:36:12,503 --> 00:36:15,631
Even Aya or Sheen don’t know.

519
00:36:16,299 --> 00:36:17,675
But…

520
00:36:17,675 --> 00:36:19,378
I have a crush on Drake.

521
00:36:24,455 --> 00:36:26,582
So you like him?

522
00:36:33,024 --> 00:36:36,319
Because he’s brave.

523
00:36:38,711 --> 00:36:41,277
Yes, he’s handsome and smart,

524
00:36:41,741 --> 00:36:43,534
but there are a
lot of guys like that.

525
00:36:45,203 --> 00:36:46,370
But Drake?

526
00:36:49,332 --> 00:36:50,791
There’s nothing more to say.

527
00:36:50,958 --> 00:36:52,210
Drake is Drake.

528
00:36:52,460 --> 00:36:53,753
He’s the real deal.

529
00:36:54,921 --> 00:36:58,674
Even if he’s perfect, he’s still human.

530
00:37:00,218 --> 00:37:04,058
I know behind that tough exterior,

531
00:37:06,015 --> 00:37:08,851
there’s a lot of angst in him.

532
00:37:11,520 --> 00:37:14,941
I can see it in his eyes.

533
00:37:16,284 --> 00:37:19,528
I thought everything she likes about me
was only superficial.

534
00:37:20,448 --> 00:37:21,532
I was wrong.

535
00:37:22,038 --> 00:37:23,331
Other than Katrina,

536
00:37:23,553 --> 00:37:25,847
Alys is the one who gets me.

537
00:38:03,322 --> 00:38:04,323
Thanks, Neil.

538
00:38:21,212 --> 00:38:22,212
Why am I moving?

539
00:38:28,055 --> 00:38:29,765
- Drake?!
- Shhh!

540
00:38:31,559 --> 00:38:32,810
How did I get out?

541
00:38:33,185 --> 00:38:34,353
Why are you carrying me?!

542
00:38:35,563 --> 00:38:36,647
Where’s Neil?

543
00:38:43,279 --> 00:38:44,572
Sir! What are you—?!

544
00:38:44,739 --> 00:38:45,906
Shhh!

545
00:38:55,499 --> 00:38:57,977
What happened?
Why are you carrying me?

546
00:38:58,002 --> 00:39:00,087
How did I get out?
Where’s Neil?!

547
00:39:00,112 --> 00:39:01,112
Ouch!

548
00:39:01,904 --> 00:39:02,904
That hurts!

549
00:39:04,240 --> 00:39:05,616
Why did you drop me?

550
00:39:11,390 --> 00:39:12,433
You’re noisy.

551
00:39:12,600 --> 00:39:14,977
You could’ve warned
me before dropping me!

552
00:39:16,312 --> 00:39:17,312
Tss.

553
00:39:21,275 --> 00:39:22,275
Hop on.

554
00:39:32,536 --> 00:39:33,079
What the hell?

555
00:39:33,079 --> 00:39:36,207
Are you trying to kill me or
are you trying to suffocate me to death?

556
00:39:53,974 --> 00:39:54,974
You’re weird.

557
00:39:57,464 --> 00:39:59,605
What are you talking about?
You’re weirder.

558
00:40:00,334 --> 00:40:01,334
Tss.

559
00:40:03,734 --> 00:40:04,734
Hop on.

560
00:40:05,903 --> 00:40:06,903
No!

561
00:40:06,987 --> 00:40:07,987
Hop on.

562
00:40:08,012 --> 00:40:09,012
No way!

563
00:40:09,365 --> 00:40:10,950
You might drop me again!

564
00:40:11,450 --> 00:40:13,077
I can go home on my own!

565
00:40:13,619 --> 00:40:14,619
Bye!

566
00:40:32,596 --> 00:40:34,526
Stop following me!
Go home!

567
00:40:39,855 --> 00:40:41,565
I said stop!

568
00:40:55,035 --> 00:40:57,580
Why can’t he go home?
As if he’s really concerned!

569
00:40:57,997 --> 00:41:01,125
If he hadn’t dropped me,
I’d be home by now!

570
00:41:04,462 --> 00:41:06,964
Just go! I’m fine! Go home!

571
00:41:12,136 --> 00:41:14,054
Why can’t he –
go home!

572
00:41:18,500 --> 00:41:20,203
Are you really not going home?!

573
00:41:20,603 --> 00:41:21,812
Go home!

574
00:41:29,904 --> 00:41:31,255
Why are you still here?!

575
00:41:31,280 --> 00:41:32,490
Leave!

576
00:41:33,585 --> 00:41:34,585
My coat.

577
00:41:35,242 --> 00:41:36,994
Huh? Isn’t this Neil’s?

578
00:41:38,746 --> 00:41:39,747
Alys!

579
00:41:40,805 --> 00:41:42,333
Uh…Mom…Dad...

580
00:41:42,541 --> 00:41:43,709
Why are you home just now?!

581
00:41:43,792 --> 00:41:45,669
We’ve been trying to reach you all night!

582
00:41:45,711 --> 00:41:47,379
We couldn’t sleep!

583
00:41:47,713 --> 00:41:48,881
We were so worried!

584
00:41:49,256 --> 00:41:50,256
We couldn’t sleep!

585
00:41:53,719 --> 00:41:56,305
Why do you look like that?
What happened to you?

586
00:42:28,641 --> 00:42:29,641
Sheen…

587
00:42:34,385 --> 00:42:35,928
You want me to be happy?

588
00:42:36,293 --> 00:42:39,087
Then tell Alys to
stay away from Drake.

589
00:42:40,140 --> 00:42:43,936
Even if he’s perfect,
he’s still human.

590
00:42:44,436 --> 00:42:50,776
I know behind that tough
exterior, there’s a lot of angst in him.

591
00:42:52,444 --> 00:42:54,196
Am I not annoying?

592
00:42:55,573 --> 00:42:56,573
You’re annoying.

593
00:42:58,701 --> 00:42:59,701
But that’s fine.

594
00:43:01,078 --> 00:43:02,078
I can see it

595
00:43:03,455 --> 00:43:04,455
in his eyes.

596
00:44:13,150 --> 00:44:16,612
On the next episode of
Seducing Drake Palma

597
00:44:16,637 --> 00:44:18,013
Didn’t we already
talk about this?!

598
00:44:18,428 --> 00:44:20,180
I thought you wanted
me to be happy?!

599
00:44:20,671 --> 00:44:22,590
Then tell Alys to back off!

600
00:44:23,452 --> 00:44:24,452
Alys!

601
00:44:25,005 --> 00:44:26,005
Sheen.

602
00:44:30,168 --> 00:44:31,168
Excuse me.

603
00:44:37,393 --> 00:44:39,228
Can we talk after dismissal?

604
00:44:40,177 --> 00:44:41,177
Alys,

605
00:44:41,991 --> 00:44:43,117
dad wants to see you.

606
00:44:44,765 --> 00:44:46,183
I’ll see you after dismissal.

607
00:44:49,884 --> 00:44:51,344
You’re my girlfriend.

608
00:44:52,064 --> 00:44:55,194
Act like one.
